<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>wǒ men suǒ xìn de shén 迦南106</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 wǒ men suǒ xìn de shén yòng hǔ kǒu liàng qióng cāng wǒ men suǒ xìn de shén yòng shǒu xīn liàng zhū shuǐ
 zài gǔ zhōng kāi quán yuán ràng shā mò biàn shuǐ chí fán shì dōu néng shuō yǒu jiù yǒu mìng lì jiù lì
 zhāng kāi nǐ de kǒu tā jiù gěi nǐ chōng mǎn qí qiú tā jiù gěi nǐ kòu mén jiù gěi nǐ kāi mén
 nǐ kě bù yào yí huò píng zhe xìn xīn qiú tā bì jiāng tiān guó de fēng fù quán néng cì gěi nǐ</lyrics>
<hymn_number>106</hymn_number>
<author>lǚ xiǎo mǐn</author>
</song>